Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.59,0:07:08.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真好听啊 大铁
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.37,0:07:11.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…但是很紧张
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.43,0:07:13.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,平时没怎么唱过嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.06,0:07:15.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是第一次吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.61,0:07:18.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为你想 平时没什么机会能唱歌的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.49,0:07:27.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁？去哪里？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.48,0:07:28.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,方便一下
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.31,0:07:32.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来是谁？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.90,0:07:33.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.98,0:07:37.88,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「妈妈抱★小可爱」
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.40,0:07:40.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个 我想你会唱的就点了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.95,0:07:43.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁会唱啊 这种小众向的动画歌曲
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.67,0:07:51.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你选什么流行歌曲啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.37,0:07:53.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算是我也会看场合啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.40,0:07:55.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行 你给我唱动画歌曲 动画歌曲
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.61,0:07:58.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且要唱你强烈推荐的那个
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.49,0:07:59.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么羞辱玩法啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.12,0:08:10.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.95,0:08:28.37,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs16}{\an7}此方她们在301房间，而仁他们是在304房间…差三间仁你怎么走错的…\N此时此方她们正好唱到第9首 也就是幸运星第9集的ED 小泉今日子的名曲《木枯らしに抱かれ》
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.94,0:08:27.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（歌）
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.23,0:09:06.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唱得还行 曲子也一般般 一点意思都没
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.77,0:09:26.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 御厨 回来的正好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.08,0:09:28.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帮忙点个柠檬汁
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.05,0:09:29.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.88,0:09:37.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…麻烦送份柠檬汁来
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.02,0:09:46.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么样？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.60,0:09:53.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么歌曲啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.50,0:09:55.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,15年前的OVA动画
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.33,0:09:58.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「妖兽机神——混沌之刃」的插入歌
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.26,0:10:00.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,与你 run away
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.05,0:10:03.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是我推荐的歌 混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.36,0:10:05.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冷场了吧 我就说冷场了吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.39,0:10:06.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别小看OTAKU 笨——蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.14,0:10:07.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吵死了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.05,0:10:09.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,贵子好差劲
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.70,0:10:11.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下一个是谁？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.22,0:10:13.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…是我
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.36,0:10:17.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还没选好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.17,0:10:21.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是第一次来…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.21,0:10:24.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就和我对唱吧 啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.96,0:10:25.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来嘛来嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.15,0:10:27.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那样的话还不如一个人唱
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.48,0:11:03.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.70,0:11:06.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,微妙…想不出能说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.89,0:11:09.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要说的话还真是有御厨的风格呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.34,0:11:17.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打扰了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.32,0:11:21.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是客人点的柠檬汁
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.03,0:11:23.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的 谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.89,0:11:25.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请让我收拾一下空杯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.33,0:11:28.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 这个也请收去
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.04,0:11:29.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.57,0:11:32.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请让我清理一下桌子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.55,0:11:37.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,告辞了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.25,0:11:46.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}再来一首 再来一首
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.22,0:11:46.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.41,0:11:55.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,御厨他飞奔出去了啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.13,0:11:59.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了 因为那太难为情了…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.73,0:12:02.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,后半完全溃不成军呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.35,0:12:06.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过能唱到最后也很不容易了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.31,0:12:13.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下一个是薙吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.80,0:12:17.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 总觉得兴奋起来了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.10,0:12:22.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这份胆力稍微分给仁一点就好了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.95,0:12:27.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 但是现在这样已经足够了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.59,0:12:31.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,薙已经分给仁很多了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.10,0:12:34.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？怎么说？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.78,0:12:37.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为就在不久前
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.77,0:12:40.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁会在别人面前唱歌还是无法想象的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.07,0:12:42.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是那样吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.44,0:12:46.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 和薙一起住后 似乎有些不一样了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.88,0:12:59.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别太在意
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.97,0:13:05.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为是第一次 不顺利也是当然的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.22,0:13:09.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不也是第一次…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.96,0:13:13.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话是这么说…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.19,0:13:19.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大铁真好呢 什么都拿手
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.81,0:13:23.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像我完全就是半吊子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.50,0:13:29.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要着急 慢慢地进步就很好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.96,0:13:33.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很多事因人而异
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.75,0:13:35.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大铁…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.72,0:13:37.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唱歌也是 画画也是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.85,0:13:42.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你一定也有自己的长处
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.30,0:14:02.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大铁 接下来是唱什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.00,0:14:05.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？还有下一首吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.70,0:14:07.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我唱了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.93,0:14:12.82,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「哼哈食品 Hello大豆之歌」
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.40,0:14:46.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…那歌是啥？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.70,0:14:49.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼哈食品 Hello大豆之歌
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.18,0:14:51.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦哦 那首广告歌啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.39,0:14:53.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为…为什么会知道那种歌啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.94,0:14:55.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在TATSUYA里有放
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.94,0:14:55.66,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（TATSUYA：这应该是 TSUTAYA 出租光碟的地方）
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.16,0:14:58.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,超市「尻毛屋」的主题歌我也会唱！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.16,0:14:58.24,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（这写法实在是太不雅了…）
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.59,0:15:01.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,基本上薙只会学这种歌
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.66,0:15:03.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正值青春年华 却无半分魅力
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.18,0:15:05.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪里…是哪里的TATSUYA？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.99,0:15:08.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正值青春年华 却无半分魅力…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.26,0:15:10.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽说在你们兴头上打扰很抱歉…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.43,0:15:13.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来轮到前辈了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.56,0:15:13.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.43,0:15:19.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚那么不留情的评价每个人 自己想必十分了得吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.97,0:15:22.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么就让大家见识一下实力吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.14,0:15:23.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.60,0:15:26.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊呀 讨厌 秋叶君
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.13,0:15:29.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,贵子一唱起歌来可不得了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.14,0:15:32.62,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「纯爱世纪」
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.82,0:16:12.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好恶…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.30,0:16:14.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好恶…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.55,0:16:17.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好恶…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.33,0:16:18.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但好赞…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.02,0:16:20.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好赞但好恶…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.97,0:16:27.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忏悔妹妹 去哪里？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.01,0:16:29.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,补个妆
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.34,0:16:41.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么样？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.26,0:16:42.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你问我怎么样…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.61,0:16:44.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真头痛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.23,0:16:46.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,觉得怎么样？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.26,0:16:49.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算你把问题扔给我也…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.76,0:16:53.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,与平日的声音相比既像又不像的动画声线…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.00,0:16:56.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么连动作都那么完美…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.97,0:17:01.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 刚才的歌就算当作单曲的一部分也是质量上等的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.00,0:17:05.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,适合唱这个歌的只有十几岁的人吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.78,0:17:06.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我怎么不是十几岁的了！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.36,0:17:10.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,童心未泯啊 童心
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.81,0:17:18.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 原来如此 童心未泯啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.03,0:17:20.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,童心也确实说得通呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.03,0:17:24.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们认同个什么劲啊 我喜欢有什么不可以的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.12,0:17:28.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难得想压个轴表现一下
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.28,0:17:31.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然来那种惊天巨雷 犯规啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.83,0:17:35.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你没什么拿手的歌吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.40,0:17:42.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？在卡拉OK唱童谣不被当成脑袋秀逗了么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.81,0:17:49.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了啦 说过火了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.57,0:17:54.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 就让我自由发挥了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.20,0:17:58.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让那孩子喜欢上也合你的心愿吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.53,0:18:03.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么还想要继续唱啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.05,0:18:06.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为没人唱嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.74,0:18:09.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下一个应该是忏悔妹妹…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.27,0:18:12.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没回来呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.49,0:18:14.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被雷跑了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.32,0:18:17.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这话是什么意思啊 姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.24,0:18:21.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回来得真晚呢 去干什么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.97,0:18:23.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍微开了下作战会议
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.72,0:18:28.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看上去似乎是轮到我出场了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.42,0:18:30.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 按顺序来的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.61,0:18:34.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歌声能够唱出一个人的内心
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.14,0:18:39.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像这样的场合 是了解彼此的绝好机会
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.38,0:18:43.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,除了那什么哼哈大豆
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.55,0:18:46.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是Hello大豆 哼哈食品的！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.68,0:18:49.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么就由被传言要发单曲的我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.15,0:18:53.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来为大家献上一曲真正的女生之歌
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.97,0:18:49.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.18,0:18:54.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有这种发展…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.65,0:18:56.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁君
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.57,0:18:56.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.02,0:19:01.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不坐在你身边也可以
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.58,0:19:06.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 请让我进到你心扉里
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.07,0:19:10.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请好好听哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.50,0:19:20.44,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「请细心地爱我吧」
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.04,0:19:48.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊呀？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.32,0:19:50.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.19,0:19:51.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好烂…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.32,0:19:53.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过好可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.85,0:19:55.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然好烂不过好可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.18,0:19:58.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,某种意义上和贵子正好相反
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.56,0:20:01.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这才叫童心未泯…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.75,0:20:22.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等下 这样是犯规的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.33,0:20:25.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里就是要这样的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.00,0:20:27.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁不是很困扰么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.14,0:20:29.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,离开点啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.57,0:20:32.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}没有这种事情的吧 仁君
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.60,0:20:34.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡拉OK原来是如此复杂的情况掺杂在一起啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.58,0:20:37.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 我不这么认为
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.90,0:20:46.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊呀 到时间了 遗憾
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.71,0:20:50.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结束了？那么开始二周目吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.34,0:20:50.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.60,0:20:53.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来是对唱了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.98,0:20:56.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(580,386)}大铁
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.87,0:20:56.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(230,386)}仁
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.23,0:20:58.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起唱吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.35,0:20:58.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.23,0:21:14.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像出了一身奇怪的汗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.17,0:21:16.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,异常疲劳
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.38,0:21:21.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁 怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.82,0:21:25.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总觉得忘记了什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.17,0:21:35.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有紫乃前辈没有唱
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.25,0:21:38.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的啊 好狡猾前辈
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.79,0:21:39.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紫乃？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.95,0:21:42.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能让她唱哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.03,0:21:44.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.45,0:21:45.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为眼睛会睁开
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.39,0:21:47.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.30,0:21:52.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 但若是无论如何…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.94,0:21:55.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都要的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（天舞宝轮！）
